    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>In ''Mr. Brooks'' Kevin Costner, right, plays a Portland, Ore., box manufacturer with a murderous (and persuasive) alter ego who takes the human form of William Hurt, left. Also on hand in this thriller by Bruce A. Evans: Marg Helgenberger, Dane Cook and Demi Moore as a wealthy heiress -- and police detective.</p>
        <p>Stephen Holden's review is on Page 8.</p>
      </block>
